---
layout: base.njk
title: "Blog | Tech Off My Plate"
description: "Practical tech tips, tool walkthroughs and real client stories for solopreneurs and small business owners, from Tech Off My Plate."
permalink: /blog/
---
<section class="blog-list">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="eyebrow">From The Blog</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">Tips, tools and real client stories</h2>
    <div class="rule"></div>

    <div style="margin-top:30px;">
      {% for post in collections.blog | reverse %}
      <a class="post-card" href="{{ post.url }}">
        <div class="post-date">{{ post.data.date | readableDate }}</div>
        <h3>{{ post.data.title }}</h3>
        <p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>
      </a>
      {% else %}
      <p style="color:#7A8699;">New posts coming soon.</p>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
